<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>مَا هِيَ ٠٠؟<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَآكِلَةٍ بِغَيْرِ فَمٍ وَبَطْنٍ * لَهَا الأَشْجَارُ وَالحَيَوَانُ قُوتُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>إِذَا أَطْعَمْتَهَا عَاشَتْ وَعَاثَتْ * وَإِن أَسْقَيْتَهَا مَاءً تَمُوتُ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">ج:</span> النَّار ٠<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>مَا هِيَ ٠٠؟<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَمَا شَيْءٌ إِذَا فَسَدَا * تحَوَّلَ غَيُّهُ رَشَدَا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَإِن هُوَ ظَلَّ في دَعَةٍ * أَثَارَ الشَّرَّ حَيْثُ بَدَا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>ذَكِيُّ العِرْقِ وَالِدُهُ * وَلَكِنْ بِئْسَ مَا وَلَدَا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">ج:</span> الخَمْر ٠<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
